      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FEDERAL PLAYER (5) recorded a smart win over 400m at The Gardens in a lightning 22.50 last start. Can measure up again if runs up to latest time. SHORTY BOY (1) is a well performed dog and winner of 16 races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at Maitland (22.89). Has ability and a bold showing is expected. BUDDY BONUS (2) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fifth (25.75) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning six races. Goes well out of this box with a win and four minor placings. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. PAW GERTRUDE (3) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage 1.5 lengths away in third (30.15). Well-placed to take this out.",
